<item>
            <title>[DERBY-4959] NPE in network server trying to return a null LOB as a procedure output arg</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-4959</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The server stumbles on the following error if you try to return a null LOB as a procedure output arg:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;java.lang.NullPointerException&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.derby.impl.drda.EXTDTAInputStream.length(EXTDTAInputStream.java:280)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.derby.impl.drda.EXTDTAInputStream.isEmptyStream(EXTDTAInputStream.java:274)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.derby.impl.drda.DRDAConnThread.writeFdocaVal(DRDAConnThread.java:7930)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.derby.impl.drda.DRDAConnThread.writeFDODTA(DRDAConnThread.java:7183)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.derby.impl.drda.DRDAConnThread.parseEXCSQLSTT(DRDAConnThread.java:4179)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.derby.impl.drda.DRDAConnThread.processCommands(DRDAConnThread.java:1021)&lt;br/&gt;
	at org.apache.derby.impl.drda.DRDAConnThread.run(DRDAConnThread.java:294)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This kills the connection. I will attach a repro.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
